    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Agreed for the most part, but where do we draw the line (sorry for the bad pun). I'm not sure which plots grids makes sense on. I guess have grids for line, scatter, density. No grid for box. On barplots I usually only have gridlines along the `y` axis, but I'm not sure that's the best default. And which ones do we fall back to rcParams on?\n"
